name: DAGMAR Marketing
overview: DAGMAR Marketing provides online marketing expertise to business owners to help them generate leads. Our services include search engine optimization (SEO) and click advertising through search engine marketing (SEM). We work with our clients to analyze traffic to their websites, then develop custom website optimization plans to convert traffic into qualified leads. We focus on helping established companies effectively invest their marketing budgets in digital marketing strategies, which are driven by our customers’ ROI. DAGMAR has built a reputation for results- and data-driven marketing programs, which has earned us a client retention rate of more than 90 percent.
